{"tid":2312060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人轉投MeWe擺脫fb金剛箍  黃店群組大增 力保言論自由","createTime":"2020-12-04T14:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T02:58:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18063b67cef0dab02e9bfd7c7791ef09a1951d7d","tid":2312060,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/NNGZ5HYSDZC43AWH2FP7TKYUEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FNNGZ5HYSDZC43AWH2FP7TKYUEA%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=b00f6200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FNNGZ5HYSDZC43AWH2FP7TKYUEA%2F&h=7273772e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/NNGZ5HYSDZC43AWH2FP7TKYUEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港人轉投MeWe擺脫fb金剛箍 <br />\n黃店群組大增 力保言論自由<br />\n<br />\n【暢所欲言】美國總統大選觸發公眾對社交平台操縱言論的質疑，掀起一股「轉場」熱潮。這陣旋風近日吹到香港，有地區群組呼籲網民棄用facebook，轉投較少限制的新平台MeWe。短短兩星期有逾百個群組響應，用戶數目與日俱增，有黃店寧願付費開新專頁，只希望擺脫審查重奪網絡言論自由。有學者指出，社交平台已成爭奪政治話語權的戰場，隨便篩選言論只會遭公眾唾棄。有資訊科技專家則關注新平台欠多重認證，網絡保安或成隱憂。MeWe聲稱，11月全球有近300萬個新登記，除違法及鼓吹暴力內容外不會過濾留言，亦強調不會賣廣告或出售用戶資料。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：月費15元無廣告「買返自由值得」<br />\n記者：佘錦洪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yhL_Ic-XJqx3YnCHLXVXaBp6HBs=/1269x1414/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S5J5YC7RPBBNHMGAYGLNLM74F4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyhL_Ic-XJqx3YnCHLXVXaBp6HBs%3D%2F1269x1414%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS5J5YC7RPBBNHMGAYGLNLM74F4.jpg&h=fbbdbd51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■twitter屢過濾拜登兒子亨特電郵醜聞新聞；而特朗普於fb的帖文則被加上「需要事實查核」的標籤。<br />\n<br />\n今年的美國大選，主。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n種種舉動，引起以支持特朗普人士為主的國內保守派不滿，在譴責兩大科網巨頭操縱言論之餘，亦同時積極發掘並轉用其他社交平台，主張以Parler取代twitter、MeWe取代facebook、rumble取代YouTube等，短時間內成為熱潮，席捲整個網絡世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lypadKSklLRu_31KgPHHagmaTHI=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AA6PX4OU55DTZLUKR6AKH2INBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlypadKSklLRu_31KgPHHagmaTHI%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAA6PX4OU55DTZLUKR6AKH2INBA.jpg&h=970fe448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Antony的專頁被fb以「買賣活體動物」為由判「死刑」，他深感被屈之餘亦甚為震怒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iMu3Ze-8DrjuiA6ike5vMr6p_nU=/1600x807/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RT36KSLG4JGQJL7YINKAQUU5AQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiMu3Ze-8DrjuiA6ike5vMr6p_nU%3D%2F1600x807%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRT36KSLG4JGQJL7YINKAQUU5AQ.jpg&h=fd198ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「天下貓貓一樣貓」專頁移居MeWe，Antony覺得此平台「用落幾有趣」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美大選證fb加緊審查<br />\n<br />\n這股「轉場」熱潮傳到香港，很快就演變成針對facebook的一場行動。將軍澳地區群組「將軍澳︱烽火台」上月中發佈了一篇關於MeWe的常見問答（FAQ），呼籲街坊放棄使用facebook，轉用主張政治中立的MeWe，隨即獲各大群組轉載，訊息又在不同通訊工具中傳閱，數日內已有近百個新MeWe群組成立，數目正持續增加。<br />\n<br />\n管理員之一的Hang表示，自美國大選以來，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「更加覺得要減少對facebook嘅依賴」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，在MeWe開群至今，無論是鄰里瑣事抑或政治大事，谷友全部都能在未經篩選下暢所欲言，因此亦吸引了原facebook群組裏近兩成人轉場，「我相信係大家都好希望有一個言論自由嘅空間」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣感覺受屈的還有全港最大的貓友討論區「天下貓貓一樣貓」，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n最終群組雖然能夠還原，facebook卻從無正式交代「死因」，Antony亦不排除與自己的「無為而治」有關，「始終呢度有廿幾萬人，有好多唔同嘅聲音、政見好正常，我哋都冇可能睇得晒」，只要留言不涉及殘害動物，任何爭吵他都傾向不插手，於是不時會收到facebook系統通知偵測到有歧視言論，「『中國人乜乜乜』，（對於facebook規則）係曖昧嘅，係灰色嘅，但你有言論自由㗎嘛&hellip;&hellip;直頭delete咗兼唔畀機會你argue，佢咪乾手淨腳囉」。<br />\n<br />\n但群組存在的目的除分享貓經及晒貓相外，。。。。。。大家都可以亂咁吹，暫時用落係幾有趣嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n比起facebook數以萬字、分六個章節共26段的社群守則，MeWe只有16條不允許事項，主要涵蓋違法及鼓吹暴力的行為，其CEO Mark Weinstein在不同訪問中亦多次重申，尊重用戶的言論自由。"},{"pid":"fa0d8c4eff7fdd0d6977f6c340ecc0b496fecad2","tid":2312060,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"04feb1b8e17bdf313c9e0168aaa0cd8ca803d79e","tid":2312060,"uid":271205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"[MeWe移民] 請轉發!!!<br />\n<br />\n近期香港人紛紛由FB/IG轉去用新社交平台MeWe,<br />\n以下網站整合了大量生意群組/興趣群組:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mewegrouphongkong.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mewegrouphongkong.com%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=cf30f40e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mewegrouphongkong.com/</a><br />\n如果你都有開群組或幫你公司開MeWe專頁, <br />\n也可以留言給網站, 網站Admin會免費幫你將你既群組/專頁放上去網站上,等更多人可以睇到<br />\n<br />\n[MeWe好處]<br />\nMeWe優點 1：無實名制<br />\nMeWe優點 2：無廣告<br />\nMeWe優點 3：任揀Emoji回應<br />\nMeWe優點 4：近似Whatsapp的Group chat 加Facebook 出Post功能二合一<br />\n<br />\n香港人生意圈 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/39r3ozj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39r3ozj&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=bb6b5de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39r3ozj</a><br />\n香港商人國際連線 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3fQ8BSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3fQ8BSo&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=beb8314e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3fQ8BSo</a><br />\n香港網店線上生意互助谷 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33ptjna\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33ptjna&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=cb625be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33ptjna</a><br />\n網店線上生意互助社 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33r9HPq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33r9HPq&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=a8f7c904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33r9HPq</a><br />\n香港餐飲業生意圈 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3o3jqmU\" data-sr